gism', 'The use of idelalisib with other potentially hepatotoxic agents such as azole antifungal agents, macrolide antibiotics, nefazodone, ritonavir, and telithromycin should be avoided whenever possible.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/123105/', '', 'Ascorbic acid, Hydroflumethiazide, Chlorothiazide, Metronidazole, Simeprevir, Lactic acid, Methazolamide, Amphotericin B, Trichlormethiazide, Ciclopirox, Probenecid, More', 'Alpelisib, Trametinib, Dacomitinib, Tivozanib, Alectinib', 1767369485);
